<div class="container">
    <h1>Zip Recipes Upgrade</h1>
    <p>This upgrade process will convert old Zip Recipes short codes into a new, better, format.</p>
    <div class="upgrade-wrapper">
        <section id="step-1">
            <div class="alert">
                <h4>Caution:</h4>
                <p>The Upgrade process will modify all posts and pages that have recipes old shortcodes. It replaces the old shortcode with new shortcode. <br>This process is NOT reversable. Make sure you have a working backup of your website.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="checkbox">
                <label><input id="accept-upgrade" type="checkbox" autocomplete="off">I have a working backup of my website.</label>
            </div>
            <button type="button" name="action_upgrade" class="button button-primary">Upgrade Now</button>
        </section>
        <section id="step-2" >
            <div class="progress" >
                <p>Process Started ...</p>
                <p> In-progress... </p>
            </div>           
            <div class="steps-success" style="display: none;">
                <p>Congratulations! Your recipes have been updated.</p>
            </div>           
        </section>
    </div>
</div>
